Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:13.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:15.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:18.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fs110\fscy90\bord.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,100.389)}Deathmatch! The Monstrous Snowman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\fscy90\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(425,429)}Versus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs140\fscy90\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(517.167,720.389)}the Two Riders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:33.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Alps, a mountain range near the\Nborder between Italy and Switzerland,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:37.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,echoes with bells\Ncelebrating a new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.99,Italics,,0,0,0,,- Happy New Year!\N- Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to read my\Nluck in the new year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna start\Ndeciphering this code.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An unlucky card...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fortunes never come\Ntrue, Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo said my fortunes\Nare very accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting an\Nunusual message...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- An earthquake!\N- Emi, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a volcano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alps are erupting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Mika, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The avalanche is\Ncoming right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:03:01.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A series of mysterious eruptions in\Nthe Alps threw Europe into mass panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.\NThe experiment was a grand success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A toast...\Nto Shocker's great leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and to our conquest\Nof the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And a toast to Doctor Shinigami\Nand Shocker's Swiss Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No... save that toast until I've removed\Nthe greatest thorn in Shocker's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I've conquered Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how you plan\Nto conquer Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan is one of the world's\Nleading volcanic zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stimulate the magma\Nbeneath those volcanoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,causing them to erupt\None after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and throw them into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is your first target?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start with the\Nsouth of Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dig a tunnel between\NKirishima and Sakurajima
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and spark an eruption in the\NKirishima volcanic region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Japan operation\Nplans have been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Catch the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be safe now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the plans\Nyou stole from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll force it out of you!\NGet them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rider!\N- Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's come to save those\Ngirls, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't let any of\Nyou leave here alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn Kamen Rider with\Nthe power of magma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get on!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Another earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a Shocker cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Snowman,\Nmade from a modified Himalayan Yeti!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the power of my Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've killed Kamen Rider!\NI, the great Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't stand a\Nchance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowman, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A truly powerful cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:14.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Well, viewers?\NDo you remember this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:19.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's Hongo Takeshi, who once fought\NShocker as the first Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:24.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He left the protection of Japan to\NIchimonji Hayato, the second Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,while he fought Shocker's\Ndestructive plots in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Hongo!\N- Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These two girls, Emi and Mika,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:37.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,have been fighting Shocker as\NHongo Takeshi's assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is serious!\NShocker's readying a major offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A major Shocker offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the\Nclassified documents!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're planning on blowing\Nup Kyushu's volcanic zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi, Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this,\Nand go to Japan at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do\Nwhen we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the Tachibana\NRacing Club in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a man named Ichimonji\NHayato, and give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:25.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the Sakurajima Earthquake\NMonitoring Station in Kagoshima Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okada! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the shouting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The movement of the needle\Nsuggests new seismic activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We might see a major\Neruption on Sakurajima again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NContact the main office in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got visitors\Nfrom Switzerland!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:29.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for riding the\Ncar ferry Saintpaulia today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:33.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We'll be traveling 887\Nkilometers at 20 knots,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:38.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,37 kilometers per hour,\Nfrom Kawasaki to Hyuga in Kyushu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and will arrive in\Ntwenty-five hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:46.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We hope you'll all enjoy\Nthis journey with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure Hayato and Taki\Ngot on board with us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not on the\Npassenger roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Think we should head back, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.\NWe already left port.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to stop\Nuntil we get to Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no swimming\Nhome, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Let's enjoy sightseeing\Non the way to Kyushu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Children are so irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a problem, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... We need to get those\Ndocuments to Hayato at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew those girls\Nwould show themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is Ichimonji\NHayato not with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Hayato and Mr. Taki\Nreally on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But how will we find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Searching a ship of this\Nsize is no easy feat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check the\Ncabins, one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey! Wait!\N- Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look down here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.\NThat's a locker, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way Hayato would\Nget such a grand cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to make sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.\NWe have the wrong room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice weather we're having, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's just not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But what a creepy old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but don't sweat it.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to be careful,\Nor they'll notice us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi's message\Nfrom Switzerland said
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that Shocker was sending a\Nhigh commander to Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's in that room, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe we should get the Shocker\Ndocuments from those Swiss girls first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we show ourselves now,\NShocker will know what we're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowman! Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I sink this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first mission is to retrieve\Nour classified documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And without being detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:25.49,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, you do\Nfortune-telling with cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet down!\NShe's trying to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ace of spades...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about this trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to sleep until\Nwe get these to Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be Hongo\NTakeshi's assistants,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm Ichimonji\NHayato's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead, then.\NI appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get inside, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hayato?\NWe've been searching everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Circumstance demanded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But where are the secret documents\Nthat Hongo sent from Switzerland?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri has them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yuri does?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because I left the\Nresponsibility with Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But go ahead and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See you! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think someone's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you after that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tell me!\N- Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you... get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker was after Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, take care of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head for the Ebino Highlands\Nthe moment the boat pulls into port.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet up again there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:07.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After 25 hours at sea, the ship pulls\Ninto port at Hyuga Harbor, Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:12.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2F2FA5&\3c&HB4B6A5&\fs60}Japan Car Ferry Hyuga Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do with that\NHayato, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He completely disappeared\Nwithout showing himself once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably waiting at the\Nhotel in Ebino Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot hide from\Nme, Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drag you out into the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H100254&\3c&HAA7812&\fs70}Ebino Highlands
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!\NThis'll make a great picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed something\Nmore comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So we swapped outfits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You and who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Suits me, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd worn jeans like\Nyou, Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lend them to me later, okay?\N- Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika! Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika! Hey, Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika! Hey, Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi... Emi's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But couldn't we\Nuse her as a decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look carefully, Snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's wearing the clothes\Nof Ichimonji's companion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but the face is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami,\NI will kill this woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then bring Ichimonji's\Ncompanion at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See that you do not fail again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kill someone\Nfor mistaken identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi! Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Run away, fast!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowman...\Nthe one you're after is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're\Nplotting here in Kyushu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't let you\Nget away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato...\NI will fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowman! Someone already\Nleaked your entire plan to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I must\Nkill you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were my orders\Nfrom Doctor Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami?\NA new Shocker commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kamen Rider...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man... of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Snowman, do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill Rider!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Magma from the deep...\Nburn Kamen Rider to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Kamen Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like this new commander\Nmay appear in Kyushu again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:55.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's attack has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:57.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With the aid of Hongo Takeshi who\Ncame from Switzerland to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:00.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato will do everything\Nhe can to stop their evil plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:05.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But what horrors does Doctor\NDeath have planned for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,60,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.70,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:15.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:16.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the magma monster Ghoster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker creates a monster capable\Nof withstanding up to 5000 degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.57,0:23:22.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and sends it to blow up\NSakurajima in Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:24.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two Riders must work\Ntogether to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:26.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:31.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Magma Monster Ghoster\NThe Great Battle of Sakurajima."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:31.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\fscy90\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}Magma Monster Ghoster\NThe Great Battle of Sakurajima
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:40.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:43.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:45.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:50.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:52.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:54.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:55.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.32,0:23:58.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:04.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:07.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:11.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:15.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Deathmatch! The Monstrous\NSnowman Versus the Two Riders
Comment: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Switzerland